    "At risk of further complicating the issue, we would also advise mentioning the programmer of the training and evaluation algorithms (the text recognition engines).",
    "An added layer that keeps coming up is that of the quality of a model, expressed in Character Error Rate (CER) and the number of tokens this has been based upon.",
